channel.description:
The title says it all!
[COLOR='Green']Message for CatzEyes: [COLOR='Red']GMod is a source engine mod mostly based around contraptions, comics, poses, and building. When you removed my other thread about this, that wasn't really necissary. This very well diserves it's own thread instead of being in the "screenshot thread". If you ever play GMod, you will understand what I mean.
